      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be passing along my pride and joy. This beauty is in truly pristine condition\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been incredibly meticulous with its upkeep, keeping it tucked away in the garage and pampered every single day. It drives like an absolute dream and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. You really have to see this one in person to believe how spotless it is!",
