      "description": "An extraordinary example of the E46 M3, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. The S54 power plant remains in peak mechanical health, featuring a recently serviced double-VANOS system and verified rod bearing clearances. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Suspension kinematics are sharpened by a meticulously tuned coilover setup, maintaining the car\u2019s legendary balance. Finished in pristine factory paint with an interior devoid of typical wear, this specimen is a concours-ready driver's car.",
