      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements and preserved in breathtaking condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of the typical stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes found on lesser examples. Every body panel is laser-straight with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of untouched luxury; the premium leather still carries that distinctive new-car aroma, and the bolsters show absolutely no signs of entry wear. All electronics, switches, and displays function with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule with all service performed by master technicians using only OEM parts. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its history as a fair-weather-only joyride. Accompanied by all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive service portfolio, this is an uncompromising choice for the buyer who demands the absolute best.",
